{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"163c2fe486","title":"解放者,還是鎮压者？","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"89a9564627","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"163c2fe486"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"2a79ce4b02","name":"陈斯骏"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c6abc40fef","type":"title","text":"解放者,还是镇压者？","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"163c2fe486"},{"id":"53d66fc03d","type":"authors","text":"北京大学陈斯骏","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"163c2fe486"},{"id":"5b3a775e9d","type":"subtitle","text":"[陈斯骏：北京大学历史系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"163c2fe486"},{"id":"287a217abc","type":"paragraph","text":"十八世纪最后几年，拿破仑统率的法国军队接连打败了地中海沿岸撒丁岛、马耳他岛和爱奥尼亚群岛等地的封建统治者。这些地区人民箪食壶浆，迎接给他们带来自由、平等、博爱的法国军队。不久，俄国沙皇的黑海舰队在海军上将乌沙科夫率领下，把法国占领的地区夺了回来，恢复了封建统治。在苏联的历史教科书和的电影作品中，乌沙科夫和沙皇军队成了“解放者”!","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"163c2fe486"},{"id":"c0391e0b14","type":"paragraph","text":"……该怎样评价拿破仑和乌沙科夫在这场斗争中的是非曲直呢?","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"163c2fe486"},{"id":"9ef2a3ba1b","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：陈斯骏提供的文章〈从北大一角看反右〉。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"163c2fe486"}],"page":{"id":"1bddff9805","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"163c2fe486","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}